parameters: [Anastasia] In this... outfit... am I supposed to serve customers?

[Scout Man] Well, but a swimsuit isn't that different, right? If it's
just that, everyone is wearing it, so it's okay.
[Anastasia] (What on earth... is going to be okay?)

[Girl 1] Hey... Didn't she look like that famous sorceress, Anastasia,
from earlier?
[Girl 2] Ah, I thought the same thing.

[Girl 1] Well... But there's no way a famous person like that would be
working in a place like this, right? She must just be a look-alike,
for sure.

[Girl 2] But she looked similar, and she seems popular already, huh,
that girl.

[Girl 1] Ahh, if she steals my big-spending customer, I'll be in
trouble~.
[Scout Man] Huh, are you a famous person?

[Scout Man] We have quite a few nobles with some circumstances, and
even students, you know.

[Scout Man] We manage the personal information of the girls properly,
and unlike working at some random tavern, we only have one customer at
a time, so you can definitely feel safe.
[Scout Man] Well, for now, just give it a try and work casually.
